description:
Claim Number 
  (Unique ID = Claim Number + Vendor ID + Processing Office)
Claim Vendor ID (originator of claim number)

Line Type:
  WC = Workers Comp
  DS  = Disability      
  GL  = General Liability
  AU  = Auto Liability
  PR  = Property
  PF = Professional Liability

Claim Type:
  " "  = AU, GL, PR, DS, PF claims that are not Incidents (Report only)                                              
  EL = Employers Liability
  MO= WC Medical Only
  IN = WC Indemnity
  IO = Incident (Report only) - regardless of line type

Claim Status:
  O  = Open
  C  = Closed
  I   = Incident Report
  L  = Deleted
  R  = Reopened

Claim Sub status:
  A = Accepted                                                                    
  C = Compromised
  F = Deferred
  D = Denied                                                                        
  J = JURIS Admin.(DS/WC Only)                          
  P = Pending  
  R = Reinstated (DS Only)
  S = Suspended (DS Only)
  T = Terminated (DS Only)
  " " = Incident

Claimant/Insured Name Type: 
  I  = Individual
 O = Organization (Last name + First name + MI)

Marital Status:
  1 = Single, Divorced, Widowed
  2 = Married
  3 = Separated
  4 = Unknown
